{"tid":329814,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"陳柏宇生日快樂！","createTime":"2017-07-20T16:15:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-20T16:15:28.000Z","uid":14730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"37f99e249b89cf6db155396b5b49716309ff5169","tid":329814,"uid":14730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T16:15:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/21/001434_a72e468c740dcdf72c0f1d9c9df372f7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F21%2F001434_a72e468c740dcdf72c0f1d9c9df372f7.jpg&h=ad35528e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n適逄尋日生日，Jason剛度完假回來，又有機會可以同一大班朋友一起慶祝。除了身邊的朋友，也有很多網民在照片下方留言祝他生日快樂。但當你以為他的社交網站很多美照時，才發現原來是錯的﹗雖然長得帥，但Jason很喜歡自毀形象，上載的照片有千百個鬼馬表情，配上搞笑的描述，你真的想不到他是那位陳柏宇。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2vFBisP\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2vFBisP&d=H3R%2FOtjhShBos1YI6J9p%2Bv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=2924bbf2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2vFBisP</a>"}]}